id":34475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T05:28:34.000Z","msg":"做完gym 唔食野就訓？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfb692b0a8ec98a4fbebcfef41e75154ee8092aa","tid":890902,"uid":24470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T05:28:57.000Z","msg":"我之前清水斷食左10日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n宜家冇晒以前嘅便秘問題，仲飲食清淡左好多<br />\n<br />\n本來想keep 16:8 但太中意食野，<br />\n變左9點後唔食， 大概11點食第一餐"},{"pid":"00d403c56ba534e75ee85e8b432590d5194aebe8","tid":890902,"uid":140454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T05:31:24.000Z","msg":"斷食唔係食少兩餐咁簡單<br />\n都要睇食乜同食幾多<br />\n乜都唔睇同普通節食無分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30192f1ae13ebaed51d0e300d305e9f8c97d9c0f","tid":890902,"uid":120019,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T05:32:40.000Z","msg":"Intermittent Fasting 講緊既係將進食時間縮短，最常見係8個鐘食野，16個鐘唔食，並唔係你地所講既只食兩餐<br />\n<br />\n最多人用既方法:<br />\n係晏晝12點到夜晚8點食野，其他時間唔吸收熱量<br />\n<br />\n係呢8個鐘你同樣要吸收你一日既卡路里(e.g. 2000)，即係唔理食幾多餐，總之要食夠/唔好食少/多過自己既目標熱量<br />\n<br />\n並唔係上面有啲人講既唔食早餐，只食兩餐。你可以9-5又得，10-6又得，係8個鐘內亦要食夠野<br />\n<br />\nIntermittent Fasting 最大既好處就係可以提高你既基礎代謝，令到你唔做運動期間既熱量消耗都可以提高"},{"pid":"d36a88d69960d7031d41024856fb57ba67fa32d8","tid":890902,"uid":146340,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T05:34:02.000Z","msg":"啲另類療法信徒同邪教有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e27b616200cb6987f80edc601f2c45b9bb514604","tid":890902,"uid":108579,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d36a88d69960d7031d41024856fb57ba67fa32d8","tid":890902,"uid":146340,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T05:34:02.000Z","msg":"啲另類療法信徒同邪教有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T05:35:12.000Z","msg":"冇<br />\n不過if有 data support 有埋moa hypothesis咁解"},